txt.en: A bounty notice asks you to seek out a goblin that has been seen lurking around Veithhól in Misthallow.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest has a one hour time limit. The timer will begin upon accepting the quest.</rgb>
You remove the completed bounty from the Limlók bounty board, feeling a sense of accomplishment in your efforts to protect the Langflood.

The bounty notice reads:

'Goblins run rampant in Misthallow! By order of Skarding Wargsbane, all goblins in Misthallow are to be found and defeated immediately! A particularly troublesome goblin has been recently spotted taking refuge at Veithhól. A reward to any who can defeat it with haste!'

<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest has a one hour time limit. The timer will begin upon accepting the quest.</rgb>
You should return to Limlók and remove the completed bounty from the bounty board.
Examine the bounty and defeat goblins at Veithhól
Return to Limlók and remove the completed bounty
